CryptoTrend - Top 10 Trending Cryptocurrencies
A Python script that fetches and visualizes the top 10 trending cryptocurrencies over the past 24 hours using the CoinGecko API.
Features

Retrieves real-time data for the top 10 trending cryptocurrencies.
Displays names, symbols, current prices in USD, and 24-hour price change percentages.
Generates a bar chart to visualize 24-hour price changes.

Installation

Clone the repository:
git clone https://github.com/your-username/CryptoTrend.git

Navigate to the project folder:
cd CryptoTrend

Install required dependencies:
pip install requests pandas matplotlib

Usage
Run the script to fetch and plot the trending cryptocurrencies:
python crypto_trend.py

The script will print a table of the top 10 coins with their details.
A bar chart will display the 24-hour price change percentages.

Requirements

Python 3.8+
Libraries: requests, pandas, matplotlib

Demo
(Note: Upload a screenshot of the bar chart to a demo/ folder and update the path accordingly.)

